        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">According to OECD the worldwide production of triphenyl phosphate for 2000 is estimated to be 20 000 - 30 000 tonnes. We here assume the global annual production volume to be the average of the reported range, 25 000 tonnes. 

Reference:
OECD. 2002. Screening Information Dataset, Initial Assessment Profile for SIAM 15. Retrieved from: http://webnet.oecd.org/hpv/ui/handler.axd?id=e23395dc-ed57-4822-b9c4-7178045c3c97, 15 July 2017.</productionVolumeComment>
