        <name xml:lang="en">Carbon dioxide, fossil</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated value. The values is based on a generic model. The basic principles of the model have been published in literature (Hischier 2005, Establishing Life Cycle Inventories of Chemicals Based on Differing Data Availability). The model has been updated and extended with newly available data from the chemical industry. Find more information in the dedicated report on the ecoinvent website. 

Reference(s):
Hischier, R. (2005) Establishing Life Cycle Inventories of Chemicals Based on Differing Data Availability (9 pp). The International Journal of Life Cycle Assessment, Volume 10, Issue 1, pp 59–67. 10.1065/lca2004.10.181.7
</comment>
